OL,3,CWales first in UK to introduce new
OL,4,Csafety rules around tattoos and
OL,5,Cpiercings
OL,7,FWales has become the first part of the
OL,8,FUK to introduce mandatory licensing
OL,9,Ffor practitioners of body art and
OL,10,Fspecial procedures, including
OL,11,Facupuncture, tattoos, semi-permanent
OL,12,Fmakeup, electrolysis, and body
OL,13,Fpiercings.
OL,15,FThe new rules, which came into effect
OL,16,Ftoday (Friday, 29 November), aim to
OL,17,Fenhance public safety and hygiene
OL,18,Fstandards across these popular
OL,19,Findustries.
