OL,3,CWales first in UK to introduce new
OL,4,Csafety rules around tattoos and
OL,5,Cpiercings
OL,7,FUnder the new regulations, all
OL,8,Fpractitioners ` as well as individuals
OL,9,Fin charge of premises or vehicles
OL,10,Fwhere these procedures are carried out
OL,11,F` are required to complete an
OL,12,Finfection prevention and control
OL,13,Fcourse tailored to special procedures.
OL,14,FAdditionally, their premises or
OL,15,Fvehicles must meet strict safety and
OL,16,Fhygiene standards to ensure they are
OL,17,Fcompliant with public health
OL,18,Frequirements.
