OL,4,Csafety rules around tattoos and
OL,5,Cpiercings
OL,7,FThe new licensing scheme, introduced
OL,8,Fby the Welsh Government, is designed
OL,9,Fto reduce the risks of infections,
OL,10,Fincluding blood-borne viruses, by
OL,11,Fensuring that only licensed
OL,12,Fprofessionals can carry out these
OL,13,Fprocedures in environments that meet
OL,14,Fthe highest safety standards.
