OL,3,CWales first in UK to introduce new
OL,4,Csafety rules around tattoos and
OL,5,Cpiercings
OL,7,FThere are more than 4,000
OL,8,Fpractitioners across Wales who will
OL,9,Fnow need to obtain a licence, and more
OL,10,Fthan 2,000 premises and vehicles where
OL,11,Fsuch procedures are carried out will
OL,12,Falso require official approval under
OL,13,Fthe new rules.
OL,15,FThis is expected to be a significant
OL,16,Foverhaul of the industry, with
OL,17,Fexisting businesses and practitioners
OL,18,Fneeding to apply for re-assessment
OL,19,Funder the new system.
