OL,7,FA key element of the new licensing
OL,8,Fscheme is the creation of a national
OL,9,Fregister, which will list all valid
OL,10,Flicence holders and approved premises
OL,11,For vehicles across Wales. Although the
OL,12,Fregister is live from today, local
OL,13,Fauthorities will only be able to
OL,14,Fupload information once they grant
OL,15,Findividual licences and approvals. It
OL,16,Fis expected to take several months for
OL,17,Fthe register to be fully populated.
