OL,7,FThis public register will allow people
OL,8,Fto check whether their practitioner is
OL,9,Flicensed and whether the premises they
OL,10,Fare visiting meet the necessary health
OL,11,Fand safety standards.
OL,13,FMarie Lowe, owner of Miss Rie's Tattoo
OL,14,FStudio, welcomes the change. She said
OL,15,Fmany people are unaware of the
OL,16,Fimportance of sterilisation.
