OL,7,FShe added:"It's good news for the
OL,8,Fspecial procedures industry that these
OL,9,Fnew rules are now in place. They will
OL,10,Fbe important in ensuring a consistent
OL,11,Fapproach is taken by all practitioners
OL,12,Facross Wales and our clients know they
OL,13,Fare having a procedure by a licensed
OL,14,Fperson in a safe and clean
OL,15,Fenvironment."
OL,17,FHowever, others fear the additional
OL,18,Fregulations will add more to the
OL,19,Foverall cost.
