OL,11,Fgetting acupuncture, electrolysis, a
OL,12,Fpiercing, tattoo or semi-permanent
OL,13,Fmakeup that the practitioner they use
OL,14,Fis licensed and the premises or
OL,15,Fvehicle where the procedure is
OL,16,Fperformed has been approved.
