OL,7,F"The compulsory licensing scheme
OL,8,Fensures that both clients and
OL,9,Fpractitioners are protected, and I am
OL,10,Fpleased the measures have been widely
OL,11,Fwelcomed by the industry.
OL,13,F"We want to see these special
OL,14,Fprocedures take place hygienically,
OL,15,Fsafely and in appropriate environments
OL,16,Fand the licensing scheme will provide
OL,17,Fassurance that the appropriate
OL,18,Fstandards are being met.
